ADDISON:
There are basically five steps

00:11.875 --> 00:13.500
to the IVF process.

00:13.542 --> 00:16.041
One, they stimulate
and monitor the development

00:16.083 --> 00:18.917
of healthy eggs
in the ovaries.

00:18.959 --> 00:20.959
Two, they harvest the eggs.

00:21.041 --> 00:24.000
Three, they select
and secure sperm.

00:24.041 --> 00:28.041
Four, they combine the egg
and the sperm in a lab

00:28.083 --> 00:31.041
and provide an appropriate
environment for fertilization

00:31.083 --> 00:32.959
and early embryo growth.

00:33.000 --> 00:35.834
And five,
they select--

00:35.875 --> 00:41.041
Identify the best embryos
and transfer them to the uterus.

00:41.083 --> 00:43.041
I'm at step one. Heh.

00:43.083 --> 00:45.333
How are you feeling
about that?

00:45.375 --> 00:49.000
I feel like...

00:49.041 --> 00:50.125
Heh.

00:50.166 --> 00:51.917
Like I'm at step one.

00:53.083 --> 00:54.709
I got hormones.

00:54.750 --> 00:56.625
Congratulations.
You pulled the trigger.

00:56.667 --> 00:58.000
