congratulations yet

00:58.041 --> 01:00.000
because I haven't pulled
the trigger,

01:00.041 --> 01:02.500
because the shots
go in my ass.

01:02.542 --> 01:04.250
Sam can't pull the trigger?

01:04.291 --> 01:05.875
I like to be sexy with Sam,

01:05.917 --> 01:08.083
and shots
that stimulate egg production?

01:08.125 --> 01:09.083
Not sexy.

01:09.125 --> 01:10.834
